OL,3,CPastor, 48, charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter baptism ceremony drowning death
OL,6,FA 48-year-old pastor has been charged
OL,7,Fwith gross negligence manslaughter
OL,8,Ffollowing the drowning of a man at a
OL,9,Fbaptism ceremony.
OL,11,FCheryl Bartley was charged with one
OL,12,Fcount of gross negligence manslaughter
OL,13,Fin relation to her role as a pastor
OL,14,Fduring the baptism, the Crown
OL,15,FProsecution Service (CPS) said.
OL,17,FThe CPS said the charge was linked to
OL,18,Fthe death of 61-year-old Robert Smith,
OL,19,Fwho drowned at an address in Erdington
OL,20,Fin Birmingham on October 8 2023, in a
OL,21,Fstatement issued on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
