CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775931065
OL,3,CPastor, 48, charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter baptism ceremony drowning death
OL,6,FMr Smith, from Brixton in south
OL,7,FLondon, died at the address on Slade
OL,8,FRoad.
OL,10,FMalcolm McHaffie, Head of the CPS's
OL,11,FSpecial Crime Division, said: "Our
OL,12,Fprosecutors have worked to establish
OL,13,Fthat there is sufficient evidence to
OL,14,Fbring this case to court and that it
OL,15,Fis in the public interest to pursue
OL,16,Fcriminal proceedings."
OL,18,FHe adds: "We have worked closely with
OL,19,FWest Midlands Police as it has carried
OL,20,Fout its investigation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1775931065
OL,3,CPastor, 48, charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Cafter baptism ceremony drowning death
OL,6,F"We remind all concerned that criminal
OL,7,Fproceedings against this defendant are
OL,8,Factive and that she has the right to a
OL,9,Ffair trial.
OL,11,F"It is vital that there should be no
OL,12,Freporting, commentary or sharing of
OL,13,Finformation online which could in any
OL,14,Fway prejudice these proceedings."
OL,16,FBartley, from Erdington, will appear
OL,17,Fat Birmingham Magistrates' Court on
OL,18,FThursday 14 May, the CPS said.
